#
# === Parameters
# [*jvm_mem_opts*]
#   User defined JVM Memory options to be passed to the AEM Author
#
# [*jmxremote_port*]
#   User defined Port on which JMXRemote is listening
#
# [*jvm_opts*]
#   User defined additional JVM options

